welcome to nexio

Bitcoin done Better

Nexio is a parallelized rollup solution that enhances the way Bitcoin does Business.

Our mission at Nexio is to make Bitcoin smarter and scalable-freeing it from limits and enabling a new era of decentralized finance on Bitcoin.

Speed & Security

High Throughput

Supports 30,000+ transactions per second and eliminates slow transaction times in Bitcoin.

Localized Fees

Prevent network-wide gas spikes, ensuring predictable costs (< $0.01 ) for developers and users

Specialized Security

Utilizing MoveVM's advanced safeguards and MPC-TSS to protect against vulnerabilities and improve smart contract security
